key="L4"><span begin="00:12.531" end="00:12.791">I</span> <span begin="00:12.791" end="00:13.041">miss</span> <span begin="00:13.041" end="00:13.308">you</span> <span begin="00:13.308" end="00:13.507">like</span> <span begin="00:13.548" end="00:13.811">it</span> <span begin="00:13.811" end="00:14.068">was</span> <span begin="00:14.068" end="00:14.297">the</span> <span begin="00:14.297" end="00:14.544">ve</span><span begin="00:14.544" end="00:14.687">ry</span> <span begin="00:14.794" end="00:15.024">fir</span><span begin="00:15.024" end="00:15.177">st</span> <span begin="00:15.281" end="00:16.241">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想念你 宛如初见的那个夜晚</span></p><p begin="00:17.002" end="00:18.344" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:17.002" end="00:17.223">And</span> <span begin="00:17.223" end="00:17.540">so</span> <span begin="00:17.540" end="00:17.768">it</span> <span begin="00:17.768" end="00:18.186">goe</span><span begin="00:18.186" end="00:18.344">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">事情就是这样</span></p><p begin="00:18.523" end="00:20.273" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:18.523" end="00:18.756">Every</span> <span begin="00:18.756" end="00:18.991">wee</span><span begin="00:18.991" end="00:19.225">kend,</span> <span begin="00:19.256" end="00:19.444">thi</span><span begin="00:19.444" end="00:19.507">s</span> <span begin="00:19.507" end="00:19.737">same</span> <span begin="00:19.737" end="00:20.059">par</span><span begin="00:20.059" end="00:20.273">ty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每个周末 还是同样的派对</span></p><p begin="00:20.461" end="00:24.215" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:20.461" end="00:20.737">I</span> <span begin="00:20.737" end="00:21.025">nev</span><span begin="00:21.025" end="00:21.179">er</span> <span begin="00:21.224" end="00:21.531">go</span> <span begin="00:21.531" end="00:21.714">a</span><span begin="00:21.714" end="00:22.227">lone</span> <span begin="00:22.490" end="00:22.582">and</span> <span begin="00:22.582" end="00:22.705">I</span> <span begin="00:22.705" end="00:22.914">don't</span> <span begin="00:22.914" end="00:23.204">seem</span> <span begin="00:23.204" end="00:23.467">bro</span><span begin="00:23.467" end="00:23.700">ken</span><span begin="00:23.700" end="00:24.012">heart</span><span begin="00:24.012" end="00:24.215">ed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我从不孤身一人前往 也未流露出心碎的模样</span></p><p begin="00:24.406" end="00:28.152" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:24.406" end="00:24.641">My</span> <span begin="00:24.641" end="00:24.969">friends</span> <span begin="00:24.969" end="00:25.152">all</span> <span begin="00:25.152" end="00:25.421">say</span> <span begin="00:25.421" end="00:25.641">they</span> <span begin="00:25.686" end="00:26.188">know</span> <span begin="00:26.431" end="00:26.673">every</span><span begin="00:26.673" end="00:26.921">thing</span> <span begin="00:26.921" end="00:27.175">I'm</span> <span begin="00:27.175" end="00:27.416">go</span><span begin="00:27.416" end="00:27.658">ing</span> <span begin="00:27.658" end="00:28.152">through</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的朋友们都说他们知道我正经历的一切</span></p><p begin="00:28.411" end="00:30.150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:28.411" end="00:28.646">I</span> <span begin="00:28.646" end="00:28.816">dri</span><span begin="00:28.816" end="00:28.916">ve</span> <span begin="00:28.916" end="00:29.164">down</span> <span begin="00:29.164" end="00:29.331">dif</span><span begin="00:29.331" end="00:29.544">fer</span><span begin="00:29.544" end="00:29.675">ent</span> <span begin="00:29.675" end="00:30.150">roads</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我沿着不同的道路前行</span></p><p begin="00:30.364" end="00:32.101" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:30.364" end="00:30.502">But</span> <span begin="00:30.502" end="00:30.635">they</span> <span begin="00:30.635" end="00:30.893">all</span> <span begin="00:30.893" end="00:31.141">lead</span> <span begin="00:31.141" end="00:31.232">ba</span><span begin="00:31.232" end="00:31.324">ck</span> <span begin="00:31.386" end="00:31.652">to</span> <span begin="00:31.652" end="00:32.101">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但它们最终都把我带回你你身旁</span></p><p begin="00:32.386" end="00:36.190" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:32.386" end="00:32.631">'Cause</span> <span begin="00:32.631" end="00:32.872">they</span> <span begin="00:32.872" end="00:33.127">don't</span> <span begin="00:33.127" end="00:33.377">know</span> <span begin="00:33.377" end="00:33.566">a</span><span begin="00:33.617" end="00:33.846">bout</span> <span begin="00:33.884" end="00:34.125">the</span> <span begin="00:34.125" end="00:34.624">night</span> <span begin="00:34.624" end="00:34.868">in</span> <span begin="00:34.868" end="00:35.071">the</span> <span begin="00:35.071" end="00:35.567">ho</span><span begin="00:35.567" end="00:36.190">tel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为他们不知道在酒店的那个夜晚</span></p><p begin="00:36.598" end="00:40.055" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:36.598" end="00:36.850">They</span> <span begin="00:36.850" end="00:37.093">weren't</span> <span begin="00:37.093" end="00:37.398">rid</span><span begin="00:37.398" end="00:37.606">ing</span> <span begin="00:37.606" end="00:37.837">in</span> <span begin="00:37.837" end="00:38.085">the</span> <span begin="00:38.085" end="00:38.592">car</span> <span begin="00:38.592" end="00:38.850">when</span> <span begin="00:38.850" end="00:39.074">we</span> <span begin="00:39.074" end="00:39.451">bo</span><span begin="00:39.451" end="00:39.581">th</span> <span begin="00:39.581" end="00:40.055">fell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我们双双坠入爱河 他们不在车里</span></p><p begin="00:40.302" end="00:44.058" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:40.302" end="00:40.433">Did</span><span begin="00:40.433" end="00:40.545">n't</span> <span begin="00:40.545" end="00:40.783">read</span> <span begin="00:40.820" end="00:41.062">the</span> <span begin="00:41.062" end="00:41.541">note</span> <span begin="00:41.541" end="00:41.810">on</span> <span begin="00:41.810" end="00:41.989">the</span> <span begin="00:42.044" end="00:42.294">Po</span><span begin="00:42.294" end="00:42.932">laroid</span> <span begin="00:43.020" end="00:43.481">pic</span><span begin="00:43.481" end="00:44.058">ture</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没看到宝丽来照片上的留言</span></p><p begin="00:44.536" end="00:48.376" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:44.536" end="00:44.802">They</span> <span begin="00:44.802" end="00:45.025">don't</span> <span begin="00:45.025" end="00:45.319">know</span> <span begin="00:45.517" end="00:46.017">how</span> <span begin="00:46.017" end="00:46.381">mu</span><span begin="00:46.381" end="00:46.488">ch</span> <span begin="00:46.488" end="00:46.962">I</span> <span begin="00:46.995" end="00:47.552">miss</span> <span begin="00:47.552" end="00:48.376">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他们不知道我对你的思念有多深</span></p><p begin="00:48.484" end="00:51.954" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:48.484" end="00:49.015">I</span> <span begin="00:49.015" end="00:49.419">wish</span> <span begin="00:49.471" end="00:50.340">I</span> <span begin="00:50.706" end="00:50.944">could</span> <span begin="00:50.944" end="00:51.094">f</span><span begin="00:51.094" end="00:51.954">ly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我希望我能飞翔</span></p><p begin="00:52.182" end="00:55.925" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:52.182" end="00:52.330">I'</span><span begin="00:52.330" end="00:52.459">d</span> <span begin="00:52.459" end="00:52.663">pick</span> <span begin="00:52.694" end="00:52.966">you</span> <span begin="00:52.966" end="00:53.176">up</span> <span begin="00:53.217" end="00:53.467">and</span> <span begin="00:53.467" end="00:53.665">we'd</span> <span begin="00:53.712" end="00:53.965">go</span> <span begin="00:53.965" end="00:54.324">ba</span><span begin="00:54.324" end="00:54.468">ck</span> <span begin="00:54.468" end="00:54.879">in</span> <span begin="00:54.879" end="00:55.925">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会接上你 一起回到过去的时光</span></p><p begin="00:56.389" end="00:59.913" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:56.389" end="00:56.755">I'</span><span begin="00:56.755" end="00:56.931">d</span> <span begin="00:56.931" end="00:57.293">write</span> <span begin="00:57.406" end="00:58.028">thi</span><span begin="00:58.028" end="00:58.212">s</span> <span begin="00:58.430" end="00:58.662">in</span> <span begin="00:58.662" end="00:58.785">the</span> <span begin="00:58.785" end="00:58.924">s</span><span begin="00:58.924" end="00:59.913">ky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会在天空中写下这句话</span></p><p begin="01:00.116" end="01:03.887" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:00.116" end="01:00.391">I</span> <span begin="01:00.391" end="01:00.625">miss</span> <span begin="01:00.625" end="01:00.872">you</span> <span begin="01:00.872" end="01:01.095">like</span> <span begin="01:01.141" end="01:01.391">it</span> <span begin="01:01.391" end="01:01.635">was</span> <span begin="01:01.635" end="01:01.883">the</span> <span begin="01:01.883" end="01:02.129">ve</span><span begin="01:02.129" end="01:02.319">ry</span> <span begin="01:02.401" end="01:02.625">fir</span><span begin="01:02.625" end="01:02.876">st</span> <span begin="01:02.876" end="01:03.887">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想念你 宛如初见的那个夜晚</span></p><p begin="01:04.610" end="01:05.916" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:04.610" end="01:04.846">And</span> <span begin="01:04.846" end="01:05.109">so</span> <span begin="01:05.109" end="01:05.353">it</span> <span begin="01:05.353" end="01:05.916">was</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">事情就是这样</span></p><p begin="